# Implementation Plan - AI-Powered Trading Platform

Build a comprehensive AI-driven trading platform for Forex, Crypto, and Meme Coins with automated execution and advanced risk management.

## Proposed Changes

### Project Structure
- `frontend/`: Next.js (React) application with TailwindCSS for the user interface.
- `backend/`: FastAPI (Python) service for API logic, user management, and trade execution.
- `ai_engine/`: Python-based module for market analysis, sentiment tracking, and prediction models.
- `docker-compose.yml`: Local development environment setup (PostgreSQL, Redis, RabbitMQ).

---

### [Component] Backend (FastAPI)
The backend will handle business logic, authentication, and integration with external APIs.
- #### [NEW] `backend/main.py` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/backend/main.py)
  Entry point for the FastAPI application.
- #### [NEW] `backend/models/` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/backend/models/)
  SQLAlchemy models for User, APIKey, Trade, Signal, and Prediction.
- #### [NEW] `backend/services/execution_engine.py` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/backend/services/execution_engine.py)
  Core logic for interacting with Binance and MetaTrader APIs.
- #### [NEW] `backend/services/risk_manager.py` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/backend/services/risk_manager.py)
  Automated stop-loss, take-profit, and daily loss limit checks.

---

### [Component] Frontend (Next.js)
A modern, responsive dashboard for users to monitor their portfolio and AI signals.
- #### [NEW] `frontend/components/Dashboard/` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/frontend/components/Dashboard/)
  Interactive charts and real-time data widgets.
- #### [NEW] `frontend/components/Signals/` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/frontend/components/Signals/)
  Feed of AI-generated buy/sell/hold signals.
- #### [NEW] `frontend/pages/index.tsx` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/frontend/pages/index.tsx)
  Main dashboard landing page.

---

### [Component] AI Engine
Dedicated module for data processing and machine learning.
- #### [NEW] `ai_engine/data_collector.py` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/ai_engine/data_collector.py)
  Fetches historical and real-time data from Binance, CoinGecko, and Social Media (X/Reddit).
- #### [NEW] `ai_engine/models/lstm_model.py` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/ai_engine/models/lstm_model.py)
  Long Short-Term Memory model for price trend prediction.
- #### [NEW] `ai_engine/sentiment_analyzer.py` (file:///c:/Users/User/AI/ai_engine/sentiment_analyzer.py)
  Natural Language Processing (NLP) for social media signals.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `pytest` for backend logic and AI model validation.
- `jest` + `react-testing-library` for frontend components.
- Integration tests simulating trade execution using Binance Testnet.

### Manual Verification
- Visual inspection of the dashboard responsiveness.
- Verification of 2FA flow during user registration.
- Manual trigger of "Emergency Stop" to ensure all trades are halted.
